Jobs at Career EducationBenefitsAbout Career EducationCampus Security and Consumer Information Disclosure



Working at Career Education
Career Education is a global educational company committed to quality outcomes and career opportunities for a diverse student population. We're looking for individuals who enjoy the entrepreneurial thrill of invention and who enjoy working as a team to create satisfying outcomes for our students and customers.
If you would enjoy working in a dynamic environment and are looking for an opportunity to become part of a stellar team of professionals, we invite you to apply online today.
 
Commitment to Diversity
Career Education is committed to a policy of equal employment opportunity and considers all persons without regard to age, color, disability, genetic information, marital status, national origin, race, religion, sex, sexual orientation, veteran status or any other status protected by applicable federal, state or local law.
Career Education is committed to fostering a culture that is challenging, engaging, rich in benefits, and inclusively diverse. At Career Education, we draw upon the strength of the diversity within our workforce, to meet and exceed the expectations of the diverse customers that we serve. Our company values and actively promotes diverse and inclusive participation by its leaders, members, and affiliates.
Our Employees Model Our Company Values and Behaviors
Achieving our purpose requires great people who are bright, creative, energetic and who possess the following values:

Urgency 
Professionalism 
Execution 
Continuous Improvement 
Gratitude 

Our Leaders demonstrate the following behaviors:

Accountability 
Energy & Excitement 
Communication & Feedback 
Commitment to Leadership 
Empathy 
Tactical Orientation 
Strategic Decision Making 









